dow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_cta admin_label="It''s low cost" title="It''s low cost" use_background_color="on" background_color="#ffffff" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center"]\r\n\r\nLet me show you how inexpensive it is.\r\n\r\nAll devices in the house are connected together through the  house’s existing wiring. And the network connects to the internet through our gateway. This reduces the overall complexity of the system. Your devices no longer need to have wi-fi or bluetooth, hence diminishing its cost.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/diagrama-plc.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" animation="left" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_slider admin_label="Slider" show_arrows="on" show_pagination="on" auto="on" parallax="off" auto_speed="5000"][et_pb_slide background_image="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/belerofonte.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" alignment="center" background_layout="dark"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide background_image="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/belerofonte-2.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" alignment="center" background_layout="dark" /][et_pb_slide background_image="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/belerofonte-4.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" alignment="center" background_layout="dark" /][/et_pb_slider][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Open source" title="Don''t wait for it, Do It Yourself!" use_background_color="on" background_color="#ffffff" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center"]\r\n\r\nHere is where stuff gets techie. For those who love to go a little further we are developing a shield for Arduino and Raspberry pi. Use it with our open SDK and develop your own gadgets with full PLC connectivity.\r\n\r\nWe’re looking forward to seeing what the community can do with this. It’s the power of PLC at your fingertips.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/opensource-logo.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-221" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/opensource-logo.png" alt="" width="320" height="84" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="on" specialty="off" background_color="#ed1c24" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_fullwidth_header admin_label="Team Slider" title="The Team" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center" /][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Carmelo J. Fernández-Agüera" position="Founder &amp; CEO" animation="left" background_layout="light" twitter_url="https://twitter.com/cjtechnik" google_url="https://plus.google.com/u/0/104402166369218695200/posts" linkedin_url="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=119988788&amp;authType=OUT_OF_NETWORK&amp;authToken=lCMs&amp;locale=en_US&amp;trk=tyah2&amp;trkInfo=tarId%3A1405095796639%2Ctas%3Acarme%2Cidx%3A1-1-1" image_url="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/FotoWeb.jpg" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Jose Enrique Corchado Miralles" position="Founder &amp; CEO" animation="top" background_layout="light" twitter_url="https://twitter.com/corshadows" google_url="https://plus.google.com/117608072535813849619/posts" linkedin_url="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=261532379&amp;trk=nav_responsive_tab_profile_pic" image_url="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/‪+34-606-24-47-46‬-20140705_153125.jpg" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Pablo Ramón Soria" position="Founder &amp; CEO" animation="right" background_layout="light" twitter_url="https://twitter.com/Bardo91" google_url="https://plus.google.com/u/0/101006510451174914625/posts" linkedin_url="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=227249854&amp;authType=NAME_SEARCH&amp;authToken=Km_6&amp;locale=en_US&amp;trk=tyah2&amp;trkInfo=tarId%3A1405096091131%2Ctas%3Apablo%20ramon%2Cidx%3A1-1-1" image_url="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Sin-título.jpg" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="on" specialty="off" background_color="#ed1c24" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_fullwidth_header admin_label="Greetings Slider" title="Greetings!" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center" /][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_blurb admin_label="Bolt" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#dd3333" use_circle="off" circle_color="#dd3333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#dd3333" image="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Bolt-logo-e1404299523821.jpg" icon_placement="top" animation="off" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-12 15:11:26', '2014-07-12 15:11:26', '', 2, 'http://localhost/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(239, 2, '2014-07-12 15:38:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '[et_pb_section background_color="#ed1c24" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/ddlogo.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" animation="left" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="2_3"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Call To Action" title="What is Domocracy?" use_background_color="off" background_color="#dd3333" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center"]\r\n\r\nDomocracy means Home Automation for everyone.\r\n\r\nIt''s a technology that makes home devices communicate through your house''s electrical wiring.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][et_pb_cta admin_label="Call To Action" title="Why Domocracy" use_background_color="off" background_color="#dd3333" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center"]\r\n\r\nDomocracy is a technology affordable for anyone. It is cheap and easy to use. Based on concepts like “plug &amp; play” and on mobile technologies, Domocracy brings smart technology to homes all over the world like no one before.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Faq', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2014-07-12 15:38:57', '2014-07-12 15:38:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?page_id=239', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(240, 2, '2014-07-12 15:14:55', '2014-07-12 15:14:55', '[et_pb_section background_color="#ed1c24" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/ddlogo.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" animation="left" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="2_3"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Call To Action" title="What is Domocracy?" use_background_color="on" background_color="#dd3333" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center"]<p>Today, everybody should have access to Smart Homes technology. However, existing solutions in the market are too expensive and too complex for most people to even consider it.</p><p>As a consequence, the general public has a vision that Domotics are expensive and hard to use. That’s why we have developed a technology that allows us to manufacture smart devices at the price of normal ones. We don’t expect people to buy our products because they are intelligent, but because for the same price they get extra value. This way, by the time you realise, your home will already be smart.</p><p>Why Domocracy? Domocracy is a technology affordable for anyone. It is cheap and easy to use. Based on concepts like “plug &amp; play” and on mobile technologies, Domocracy brings smart technology to homes all over the world like no one before.</p>[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Faq', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '239-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-12 15:14:55', '2014-07-12 15:14:55', '', 239, 'http://localhost/239-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
