(477, 2, '2015-01-07 13:08:49', '2015-01-07 13:08:49', 'TOP TEN OPEN SOURCE PROJECTS\n\n&nbsp;\n\nTalking about the concept of open source, its philosophy is alright, but there is nothing like seeing the examples which are more molan to know why this development model is on the rise among technology companies like us. Here we go!\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3>OpenPilot</h3>\nOpenPilot is a UAV (unmanned aerial vehicle) or more commonly known as Drone, developed by the OpenPilot open source community. This platform began in early 2010 and was created to serve for research but due to the increasing use of these drones, the platform has grown to develop complex flight plans and other multiple tools for freaks of flying machines.\nWith these drones you can put a camera like the famous (GoPro) to record yourself practicing your favorite sport, or even to record a home movie. These robots are the future! soon everyone will have one helping them to carry their bags the way home', 'Top ten ', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'top-ten', '', '', '2015-01-07 13:10:44', '2015-01-07 13:10:44', '', 0, 'http://www.domocracytech.com/?p=477', 0, 'post', '', 0),
